:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"wordpress real estate\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=223537\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:612:\"<p>Do you want the best real estate plugins for your WordPress website? Real estate websites are a fantastic business generator as they support tools and features to make property deals online. In this article, we&#8217;ll share 9 of the best WordPress real estate plugins you can use to make your website a success. Creating a [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-real-estate-plugins/\">9 Best WordPress Real Estate Plugins COMPARED (2018)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17619:\"<p>Do you want the best real estate plugins for your WordPress website? Real estate websites are a fantastic business generator as they support tools and features to make property deals online.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share 9 of the best WordPress real estate plugins you can use to make your website a success.</p>\n<h3>Creating a Real Estate Website with WordPress</h3>\n<p>WordPress is the most flexible and popular website builder on the market. Many of <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/popular-big-name-brands-using-wordpress/\" title=\"46 Biggest Brands in the World Using WordPress Actively\">the world&#8217;s top brands are using WordPress</a> for their websites.</p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll find 2 kinds of WordPress websites: WordPress.com, which is a hosted platform; and WordPress.org, which is a self-hosted solution. For more details, see our side-by-side comparison on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-com-vs-wordpress-org-one-really-better/\" title=\"WordPress.com vs. WordPress.org – Is One Really Better Than the Other?\">WordPress.com vs WordPress.org</a>.</p>\n<p>For a real estate website, you should use self-hosted WordPress.org. It&#8217;s highly flexible and offers amazing features to develop powerful websites.</p>\n<p>Before starting, you&#8217;ll need to buy a domain name and a web hosting account to install WordPress properly.</p>\n<p>Bluehost is our recommended web hosting solution. It&#8217;s one of the most popular hosting companies and is officially recommended by WordPress&#8217; core.</p>\n<p>Luckily, they&#8217;re offering IsItWP readers a free domain name, free SSL certificate, and a massive discount on web hosting.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost.jpg\" alt=\"create a blog on bluehost\" width=\"775\" height=\"483\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-218254\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost-300x187.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost-768x479.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Click Here to Claim This Exclusive Bluehost Offer &raquo;</a></p>\n<p>After purchasing web hosting, you can follow our step-by-step guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Make a Website in 2018- Step by Step (with Pictures)\">how to create a WordPress website</a>.</p>\n<p>Having said that, let&#8217;s take a look at the best WordPress real estate plugins.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/real-estate-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Real Estate Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. Real Estate Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/real-estate-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Real Estate Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/realestatepro.jpg\" alt=\"Real Estate Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223541\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/realestatepro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/realestatepro-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/realestatepro-768x297.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Real Estate Pro is a premium WordPress real estate and property listing plugin. It enables your users to add their listings, claim listings, sell properties, manage client reviews, and more. Your website&#8217;s visitors can bid for the properties, leave a note for the listing owner, contact property owners, and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/tips-get-email-subscribers/\" title=\"23 Effective Tips to Get More Email Subscribers Today\">subscribe to your lists</a> to get regular updates.</p>\n<p>The plugin&#8217;s translation-ready and fully supports <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpml/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPML\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPML</a>. It also supports third-party services like Stripe, PayPal, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mailchimp/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"MailChimp\" rel=\"nofollow\">MailChimp</a>, etc. </p>\n<p>Real Estate Pro is integrated with <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/visual-composer-website-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Visual Composer\" rel=\"nofollow\">Visual Composer</a> to quickly set up your property website and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/legit-ways-to-make-money-online-blogging/\" title=\"30 Ways to Make Money Online Blogging (On the Side) in 2018\">start making money online</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/estatik/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Estatik\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Estatik</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/estatik/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Estatik\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/estatik.jpg\" alt=\"Estatik\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223540\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/estatik.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/estatik-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/estatik-768x297.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Estatik is a free WordPress real estate plugin that can be used to add property listings on your website. You can use this plugin to create and manage fully functional real estate solutions with ease.</p>\n<p>It offers language support, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/google-maps-builder/\" title=\"Google Maps Builder Review: Easily Embed Interactive Maps\">Google Maps</a> integration, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-social-media-plugins/\" title=\"12 Best WordPress Social Media Plugins (2018)\">social media</a> icons, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-gallery-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Gallery Plugins Compared (2018)\">an image gallery</a>, real estate widget, and more. It comes with unlimited options for your property listings so you can customize and sell the properties online.</p>\n<p>Estatik has advanced filters in the search for dates, famous properties, pricing, and location. It&#8217;s a fully customizable plugin and works great with all the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/top-wordpress-themes/\" title=\"The Best and Most Popular WordPress Themes of 2018 (UPDATED)\">top WordPress themes</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-listings/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"IMPress Listings\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. IMPress Listings</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-listings/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"IMPress Listings\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/impresslistings.jpg\" alt=\"IMPress listings\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223542\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/impresslistings.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/impresslistings-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/impresslistings-768x297.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>IMPress Listings is a popular WordPress plugin for real estate websites. It offers a complete solution for beginners to advanced users to launch an online real estate business.</p>\n<p>It allows your users to add their listings with images and videos of the properties. The visual impact increases traffic on your real estate website and helps with <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-seo-tools-to-grow-your-site-traffic/\" title=\"9 Best SEO Tools to Grow Your Website Traffic, FAST!\">improving SEO</a>. You can easily customize the property listings and design beautiful listing pages with complete details, Google maps, and contact information of the listing&#8217;s owner.</p>\n<p>It fully supports IDX listing and you can also import listings from other sources. It recommends a few companion plugins to include additional features to make a truly powerful real estate website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wp-amortization-calculator/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WP Amortization Calculator\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. WP Amortization Calculator</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wp-amortization-calculator/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WP Amortization Calculator\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpamortizationcalc.jpg\" alt=\"WP Amortization Calculator\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223544\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpamortizationcalc.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpamortizationcalc-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpamortizationcalc-768x297.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WP Amortization Calculator is a premium WordPress plugin used to calculate mortgages, loans, and property financing online. It has features go above and beyond a simple mortgage calculator. It supports a lead capture tool, real estate listings, agents portal, custom property pages, email notifications, and more.</p>\n<p>It also enables you to use currency symbols and different money format choices. The <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\" title=\"7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders Compared (2018)\">drag and drop builder</a> support allows you to add a sophisticated amortization calculator anywhere on your real estate website.</p>\n<p>It has a custom widget that can be added in your widget areas. It&#8217;s translation-ready and includes flexible options to automatically calculate amortized loans.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-property/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WP-Property\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. WP-Property</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-property/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WP-Property\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpproperty.jpg\" alt=\"WP Property\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223545\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpproperty.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpproperty-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpproperty-768x297.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WP-Property is a free real estate WordPress plugin. It has the options to add property listings, manage listings, and more. It includes powerful custom options to add complete details for each property listing, like yhe number of rooms, bathrooms, capacity, parking, and other features of the property.</p>\n<p>You can create stylish property listing pages with Google Maps, real estate search, featured listings, search filters, and <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-tutorials/how-to-create-an-idx-real-estate-website-using-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"IDX listing support\">IDX listing support</a>. It suggests free WordPress real estate themes and also works great with all other themes.</p>\n<p>It has widgets, shortcodes, and other methods to show real estate listings anywhere on your WordPress website. WP-Property is a flexible plugin with translation support and it&#8217;s optimized for SEO.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/essential-real-estate/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Essential Real Estate\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Essential Real Estate</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/essential-real-estate/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Essential Real Estate\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/essentialrealestate.jpg\" alt=\"Essential real estate\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223547\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/essentialrealestate.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/essentialrealestate-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/essentialrealestate-768x297.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for a real estate plugin that allows frontend property listing submissions, then Essential Real Estate plugin is perfect. It has both backend and frontend support for listing submissions with a powerful dashboard for agents to manage their listings.</p>\n<p>It enables you to easily customize and set up a real estate website with all the features you need. Essential Real Estate plugin supports all global <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-stripe-payment-plugins-for-wordpress/\" title=\"6 Best Stripe Payment Plugins for WordPress (2018)\">payment methods</a> so you can build a real estate market online.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/birchpress/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"BirchPress\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. BirchPress</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/birchpress/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"BirchPress\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/birchpress.jpg\" alt=\"BirchPress\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223548\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/birchpress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/birchpress-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/birchpress-768x297.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>BirchPress is a WordPress <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/make-appointment-booking-system-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Make an Appointment Booking System with WordPress\">appointment booking and scheduling</a> plugin. It can be used as an addon on your real estate website to manage appointments between clients and agents.</p>\n<p>It allows you to easily <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-booking-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Booking Plugins Compared (2018)\">add a booking form</a> on your WordPress website and also integrates online payments through PayPal. It fully supports <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WooCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce</a> and all its features, so you can easily sell properties online.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wpcasa/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPCasa\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. WPCasa</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wpcasa/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPCasa\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpcasa.jpg\" alt=\"WPCasa\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223549\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpcasa.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpcasa-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpcasa-768x297.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WPCasa is a real estate plugin for WordPress websites. It features multiple themes that can be used to create a fully flexible and powerful real estate platform for users. WPCasa has an easy-to-use interface and all the settings are simple to manage in WordPress.</p>\n<p>It supports an advanced search engine with multiple filters to quickly find property listings on your real estate website. You can use the WPCasa editor to add property information, location maps, image galleries, and more details about your listings easily.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/real-estate-listing-realtyna-wpl/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPL Real Estate\" rel=\"nofollow\">9. WPL Real Estate</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/real-estate-listing-realtyna-wpl/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPL Real Estate\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wplrealestate.jpg\" alt=\"WPL real estate\" width=\"775\" height=\"299\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223550\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wplrealestate.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wplrealestate-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wplrealestate-768x296.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WPL Real Estate is another free real estate solution for WordPress websites. It features a filterable search for users to find property listings. It offers a flexible frontend dashboard for users and agents to add their listing quickly. WPL Real Estate has the options for users to add their personal profile, property locations with Google maps, create stylish listings, custom fields, and more.</p>\n<p>It works great with all the most <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/must-have-wordpress-plugins-for-business-websites/\" title=\"25 Must Have WordPress Plugins for Business Websites (Expert Pick)\">popular WordPress plugins</a> and supports IDX listings in the premium version. You can reach out to the plugin&#8217;s developer to get custom features on request.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find the best WordPress real estate plugins. You should also check out our hand-picked list of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-event-plugins/\" title=\"9 Best WordPress Events Plugins Compared (2018)\">best WordPress event plugins</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-real-estate-plugins/\">9 Best WordPress Real Estate Plugins COMPARED (2018)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-real-estate-plugins/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"h