7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27769:\"<p>Do you want the best WordPress plugins for nonprofits to add features on your site? Nonprofits need WordPress plugins that can support their cause and help them build a website on a tight budget. The perfect plugins allow nonprofits to launch their website without hiring any developer, so they can save money for what really matters: their cause.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share the best WordPress plugins for nonprofits to support your cause.</p>\n<h3>Making a Nonprofits Website with WordPress</h3>\n<p>WordPress is the most popular website builder in the world. You&#8217;ve likely noticed many of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/popular-big-name-brands-using-wordpress/\" title=\"46 Biggest Brands in the World Using WordPress Actively\">biggest brands in the world using WordPress actively</a> on their sites.</p>\n<p>When starting, you&#8217;ll encounter 2 types of WordPress sites: WordPress.com, which is a hosted platform; and WordPress.org, which is a self-hosted solution. See our detailed comparison between <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-com-vs-wordpress-org-one-really-better/\" title=\"WordPress.com vs. WordPress.org – Is One Really Better Than the Other?\">WordPress.com vs WordPress.org</a> for more information.</p>\n<p>For your site, we recommend using self-hosted WordPress.org as it has all the features and options you&#8217;ll need. If you&#8217;re already using WordPress.com, then you can <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-move-your-site-from-wordpress-com-to-wordpress-org/\" title=\"How to Move Your Site From WordPress.com to WordPress.org\">move your site from WordPress.com to WordPress.org</a>.</p>\n<p>But, first, you&#8217;ll need a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/difference-between-domain-name-and-web-hosting-revealed/\" title=\"What’s the Difference Between Domain Name and Web Hosting? (REVEALED)\">domain name and web hosting</a>.</p>\n<p>We recommend <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bluehost\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a>. It&#8217;s officially recommended by WordPress core, and 1 of the popular web hosting companies in the world.</p>\n<p>Luckily, they&#8217;re offering our users a free domain name, free SSL certificate, and a massive discount on web hosting.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost.jpg\" alt=\"create a blog on bluehost\" width=\"775\" height=\"483\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-218254\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost-300x187.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost-768x479.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Click Here to Claim This Exclusive Bluehost Offer &raquo;</a></p>\n<p>Once purchased, you can follow our step-by-step guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Make a Website in 2018- Step by Step (with Pictures)\">how to make a website</a>.</p>\n<p>Now, let&#8217;s take a look at the best WordPress plugins for nonprofits you can use on your WordPress site.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPForms\">1. WPForms</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPForms\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms.jpg\" alt=\"WPForms\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222076\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WPForms is the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Contact Form Plugins Compared (2018)\">best WordPress contact form plugin</a>. It&#8217;s super flexible and comes with great features to add a contact form, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-wordpress-donation-form/\" title=\"How to Create a WordPress Donation Form (Step by Step)\">donation form</a>, and other useful forms on your WordPress site.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wpforms-lite/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPForms Lite\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPForms Lite</a> is the free version of the plugin. It can be used by <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-small-business-website-simple-steps/\" title=\"How to Create a Small Business Website in 5 Simple Steps (2018)\">small business websites</a>, nonprofits, and blogs to add a simple contact form easily. Their paid version comes with more features and options like payment addons. </p>\n<p>WPForms integrates with all the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-email-marketing-services-compared/\" title=\"9 Best Email Marketing Services Compared (2018)\">best email marketing services</a> like <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/aweber/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"AWeber\" rel=\"nofollow\">AWeber</a>, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mailchimp/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"MailChimp\" rel=\"nofollow\">MailChimp</a>, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Constant Contact\" rel=\"nofollow\">Constant Contact</a>, and more.</p>\n<p>It also works great with payment services like PayPal and Stripe to collect online donations.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"MonsterInsights\">2. MonsterInsights</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"MonsterInsights\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights.jpg\" alt=\"MonsterInsights\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222077\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>MonsterInsights is the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-analytics-solutions-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Analytics Solutions Compared (2018)\">best WordPress analytics solution</a> on the market. It shows your website traffic stats in your WordPress dashboard. MonsterInsights has many powerful addons to customize the Google Analytics reports for your site.</p>\n<p>They offer multiple pricing plans for small-to-big websites which means you can easily use MonsterInsights on your nonprofit website to add Google Analytics in WordPress.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/givewp/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"GiveWP\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. GiveWP</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/givewp/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"GiveWP\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/givewp.jpg\" alt=\"GiveWP\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222707\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/givewp.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/givewp-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/givewp-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>GiveWP is an excellent WordPress nonprofits plugin. It comes with all the features you&#8217;ll need to accept online donations, manage the money given, and more within your WordPress dashboard. You can easily create a donation form and integrate a payment gateway to collect donations from users.</p>\n<p>Speaking of payment gateways, GiveWP can be easily connected with the most popular payment services, like PayPal. On top of that, you can also connect your donation form with the popular email services, including AWeber and MailChimp.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"OptinMonster\">4. OptinMonster</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"OptinMonster\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/optinmonster.jpg\" alt=\"OptinMonster\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222709\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/optinmonster.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/optinmonster-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/optinmonster-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>OptinMonster is the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-lead-generation-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Lead Generation Plugins Compared (2018)\">best WordPress lead generation plugin</a> in the world. You can use this plugin on your nonprofit site to make sure visitors donate to your cause before leaving your site.</p>\n<p>It offers multiple optin popup styles including slide in, sidebar, lightbox, and more. OptinMonster has helped many businesses and nonprofits to grow their subscribers exponentially.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/easy-digital-downloads/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Easy Digital Downloads\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. Easy Digital Downloads</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/easy-digital-downloads/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Easy Digital Downloads\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/easydigitaldownloads.jpg\" alt=\"Easy Digital Downloads\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222708\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/easydigitaldownloads.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/easydigitaldownloads-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/easydigitaldownloads-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Easy Digital Downloads is one of the most popular <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress eCommerce Plugins Compared (2018)\">WordPress eCommerce plugins</a>. It allows you to sell digital downloads, like eBooks, to collect money for your nonprofit cause. </p>\n<p>Easy Digital Downloads has powerful addons to integrate payment gateways, services, and more.</p>\n<p>It works great on all the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/top-wordpress-themes/\" title=\"The Best and Most Popular WordPress Themes of 2018 (UPDATED)\">best WordPress themes</a>. It&#8217;s flexible and easy to set up on your site.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-super-cache/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WP Super Cache\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. WP Super Cache</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-super-cache/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WP Super Cache\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpsupercache.jpg\" alt=\"WP Super Cache\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222725\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpsupercache.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpsupercache-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpsupercache-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WP Super Cache is a popular <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-caching-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Caching Plugins Compared (2018)\">caching plugin for WordPress</a> sites. It&#8217;s free to download and use. It comes with amazing caching features that&#8217;ll help you improve the performance of your nonprofit website.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/wp-super-cache/\" title=\"WP Super Cache Review 2018: Is It the Best WordPress Caching Plugin?\">WP Super Cache</a> offers page cache, CDN support, cache pre-loading, gzip compression, and more. It&#8217;s easy to set up and all settings are beginner-friendly.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/sucuri/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Sucuri Scanner\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Sucuri</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/sucuri/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Sucuri Scanner\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/sucuri.jpg\" alt=\"Sucuri\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222080\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/sucuri.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/sucuri-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/sucuri-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Sucuri is the top <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-security-plugins-compared/\" title=\"6 Best WordPress Security Plugins Compared (2018)\">WordPress security plugin</a>. It creates a secure wall between your users and your website to protect you from unwanted visitors. <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/sucuri/\" title=\"Sucuri Review 2018: Why We Love Sucuri + Pros and Cons\">Sucuri</a> has amazing features that&#8217;ll keep your website secure from malware and hackers.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s a recommended plugin for nonprofit sites who accept online donations to maintain security for your donors.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/updraftplus/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"UpdraftPlus\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. UpdraftPlus</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/updraftplus/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"UpdraftPlus\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/updraftplus.jpg\" alt=\"UpdraftPlus\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222079\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/updraftplus.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/updraftplus-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/updraftplus-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>UpdraftPlus is a popular <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-backup-plugins-compared/\" title=\"9 Best WordPress Backup Plugins Compared (2018)\">backup plugin for WordPress</a> sites. It allows you to easily <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/easily-backup-wordpress-site-step-step/\" title=\"How to Easily Back Up Your WordPress Site (Step by Step)\">back up your WordPress site</a>.</p>\n<p>Once you&#8217;ve created your nonprofit site, you&#8217;ll want to make sure it&#8217;s up and running, always. <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/updraftplus-review/\" title=\"UpdraftPlus Review: Is It the Best WordPress Backup Plugin?\">UpdraftPlus</a> helps you maintain regular backups of your site. It also allows you to easily restore your site from the backups anytime you need to.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Yoast SEO\" rel=\"nofollow\">9. Yoast SEO</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Yoast SEO\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/yoastseo.jpg\" alt=\"Yoast SEO\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222083\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/yoastseo.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/yoastseo-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/yoastseo-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Yoast SEO is the most popular WordPress SEO plugin on the market. It helps you optimize your website for search engines, so you&#8217;ll attract the best visitors who actually want to support your cause. <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/yoast-seo/\" title=\"Yoast SEO Review 2018: Is It the Best WordPress SEO Plugin?\">Yoast SEO</a> has many features that can be used to improve your search engine rankings.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/envira-gallery/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Envira Gallery\" rel=\"nofollow\">10. Envira Gallery</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/envira-gallery/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Envira Gallery\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/enviragallery.jpg\" alt=\"Envira Gallery\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222078\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/enviragallery.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/enviragallery-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/enviragallery-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Envira Gallery is one of the top <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-gallery-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Gallery Plugins Compared (2018)\">WordPress image gallery plugins</a>. Many nonprofits want to show their images to new visitors to convince them to donate, which is why <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/envira-gallery/\" title=\"Envira Gallery Review 2018 – The Best WordPress Gallery Plugin\">Envira Gallery</a> is an important plugin for the nonprofit sites.</p>\n<p>It allows you to present your photos in beautiful, professional image galleries. It has amazing features like lightbox popup, masonry galleries, polaroid effects, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/testimonials-widget/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Testimonials Widget\" rel=\"nofollow\">11. Testimonials Widget</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/testimonials-widget/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Testimonials Widget\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/testimonialwidgets.jpg\" alt=\"Testimonials Widget\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222727\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/testimonialwidgets.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/testimonialwidgets-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/testimonialwidgets-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Testimonials Widget is a free WordPress testimonials plugin. It&#8217;s important for nonprofit sites to display testimonials from their donors. The plugin is beginner-friendly and easy to set up.</p>\n<p>It allows you to show testimonials anywhere, including posts, pages, and widget-ready areas. You can add the testimonials widget in your sidebar, footer, or any other widget-supported sections in WordPress.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/quick-and-easy-faqs/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Quick and Easy FAQs\" rel=\"nofollow\">12. Quick and Easy FAQs</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/quick-and-easy-faqs/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Quick and Easy FAQs\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/quickeasyfaqs.jpg\" alt=\"Quick and Easy FAQs\" width=\"785\" height=\"405\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222728\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/quickeasyfaqs.jpg 785w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/quickeasyfaqs-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/quickeasyfaqs-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 785px) 100vw, 785px\" /></a></p>\n<p>As the name suggests, Quick and Easy FAQs is an easy-to-use WordPress FAQs plugin. You can use this plugin to add frequently asked questions, with answers, onto your nonprofit site. It saves the time for you and your visitors. The plugin has many templates to present FAQs beautifully.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tablepress/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"TablePress\" rel=\"nofollow\">13. TablePress</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tablepress/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"TablePress\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/tablepress.jpg\" alt=\"TablePress\" width=\"775\" height=\"356\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222729\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/tablepress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/tablepress-300x138.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/tablepress-768x353.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>TablePress is a free WordPress plugin to add tables, using a simple drag and drop interface, on your site. You can use these tables on your nonprofit site to display donation charts and other stats to your visitors.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/google-calendar-events/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Simple Calendar – Google Calendar Plugin\" rel=\"nofollow\">14. Simple Calendar</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/google-calendar-events/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Simple Calendar – Google Calendar Plugin\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/simplecalendar.jpg\" alt=\"Simple Calendar\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222730\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/simplecalendar.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/simplecalendar-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/simplecalendar-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Simple Calendar is a Google Calendar plugin that lets you to create events and display them on your nonprofit site. It allows your visitors to subscribe to the calendar, and they&#8217;ll get notifications for new events.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/forget-about-shortcode-buttons/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Forget About Shortcode Buttons\" rel=\"nofollow\">15. Forget About Shortcode Buttons</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/forget-about-shortcode-buttons/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Forget About Shortcode Buttons\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/forgetaboutshortcodebuttons.jpg\" alt=\"Forget About Shortcode Buttons\" width=\"775\" height=\"396\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222739\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/forgetaboutshortcodebuttons.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/forgetaboutshortcodebuttons-300x153.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/forgetaboutshortcodebuttons-768x392.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Forget About Shortcode Buttons is a free WordPress plugin to add stunning buttons onto your nonprofit site. You need to add multiple call-to-action buttons on different pages and posts to make people visit your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-landing-page-plugins/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Landing Page Plugins That Convert (2018)\">landing pages</a> or donation forms. This unique plugin will help you easily add buttons without the help of shortcodes.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/polylang/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Polylang\" rel=\"nofollow\">16. Polylang</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/polylang/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Polylang\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/polylang.jpg\" alt=\"Polylang\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222744\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/polylang.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/polylang-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/polylang-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Polylang is a WordPress plugin that offers bilingual and multilingual support. It allows you to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/easily-create-multilingual-wordpress-website/\" title=\"How to Easily Create a Multilingual WordPress Website (Step by Step)\">create a multilingual nonprofit site</a>, so anyone in the world can read and follow your content in their own language. It allows your visitors to easily switch the website&#8217;s language into their own language.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/floating-social-bar/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Floating Social bar\" rel=\"nofollow\">17. Floating Social bar</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/floating-social-bar/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Floating Social bar\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/floatingsocialbar.jpg\" alt=\"Floating Social Bar\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222748\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/floatingsocialbar.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/floatingsocialbar-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/floatingsocialbar-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you want to add social sharing buttons onto your WordPress site in a beautiful and modern style, then you&#8217;ll need the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/floating-social-bar/\" title=\"Floating Social Bar\">Floating Social Bar</a> plugin. It&#8217;s a free <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-social-media-plugins/\" title=\"12 Best WordPress Social Media Plugins (2018)\">social sharing plugin</a> for nonprofit sites to easily share their cause on social media platforms. Your visitors can share the pages and posts on social media channels quickly with just 1 click.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tweet-old-post/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Revive Old Post\" rel=\"nofollow\">18. Revive Old Post</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tweet-old-post/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Revive Post\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/revivepost.jpg\" alt=\"Revive Post\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222749\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/revivepost.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/revivepost-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/revivepost-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Revive Old Post is another interesting WordPress plugin that automatically shares your old posts on social media. It saves you time via its automation process. You should use this plugin on your nonprofit site to promote your old posts and keep your social sites engaged.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mappress-google-maps-for-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"MapPress Maps\" rel=\"nofollow\">19. MapPress Google Maps</a></h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/mappress.jpg\" alt=\"MapPress Google Maps\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222750\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/mappress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/mappress-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/mappress-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>MapPress Google Maps is a WordPress plugin for sharing the location of your nonprofit centre. It features easy-to-embed maps that you can place on your WordPress pages and posts. It allows you to mark destinations, add directions, and more.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find best WordPress plugins for nonprofits. You should also check out our hand-picked <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-responsive-wordpress-themes/\" title=\"50+ Best Responsive WordPress Themes\">best responsive WordPress themes</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-plugins-nonprofits/\">19 Best WordPress Plugins for Non-profits &#038; Charities</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-plugins-nonprofits/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"How to Properly Add Code Snippets to Your WordPress Site\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xm